gate: OPEN
task: S74-TD5
title: Fix Time Selection Popup Behavior
description: |
  Fix the time selection popup to show clock by default and improve UX:
  - Change default view from slider to clock
  - Keep popup open after drag-end on slider
  - Allow user to select time and review before confirming
  - Add/ensure Done button for final confirmation
  - Make slider secondary/optional option

acceptance:
  - Time popup opens with clock view by default
  - Popup remains open after slider interaction
  - User can review selected time before confirming
  - Done button properly closes popup with selected time
  - Slider is available as secondary option

requires: []
estimated: 2 hours
